Package estimate.view

Class GameUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • estimate.view.GameUI
  • public class GameUI
extends java.lang.Object
    Main GUI of the game. Contains all the methods to display selected options by player. GameUI is called by the main menu, GUI. The logic is controlled by GameLogic.
    Since:
    Nov 4, 2019
